messageBody:
In the 'Alice in Wonderland' tutorial at Malt's web
page, some QS letters are clearly italicized.
Perhaps this is an algorithmic extension of the
font because of lack of a true italic version, but it
reads quite well in the few examples.

http://members.optusnet.com.au/~malt99/project_quickscript_website/

--- Ted Larson Freeman <freeman@...>
wrote:
> Yes, slanting to the right is what I have in mind.
> But if it doesn't
> look good, c'est la vie.


===========
Never insult anyone by accident.
- Robert A. Heinlein
